text: Laura Tramuns Tripiana (born February 19, 1970 in Badalona, Barcelona) is a swimmer and track and field athlete from Spain. She has a physical disability and is a S8/T46 type athlete. She competed at the 1996 Summer Paralympics and 2000 Summer Paralympics in swimming.
